name: __ETextureColorSpace
doc: List of (source) texture color spaces, matching the list in ColorManagementDefines.h.

TCS_sRGB: sRGB / Rec709 (BT.709) color primaries, with D65 white point.
TCS_Rec2020: Rec2020 (BT.2020) primaries with D65 white point.
TCS_ACESAP0: ACES AP0 wide gamut primaries, with D60 white point.
TCS_ACESAP1: ACES AP1 / ACEScg wide gamut primaries, with D60 white point.
TCS_P3DCI: P3 (Theater) primaries, with DCI Calibration white point.
TCS_P3D65: P3 (Display) primaries, with D65 white point.
TCS_REDWideGamut: RED Wide Gamut primaries, with D65 white point.
TCS_SonySGamut3: Sony S-Gamut/S-Gamut3 primaries, with D65 white point.
TCS_SonySGamut3Cine: Sony S-Gamut3 Cine primaries, with D65 white point.
TCS_AlexaWideGamut: Alexa Wide Gamut primaries, with D65 white point.
TCS_CanonCinemaGamut: Canon Cinema Gamut primaries, with D65 white point.
TCS_GoProProtuneNative: GoPro Protune Native primaries, with D65 white point.
TCS_PanasonicVGamut: Panasonic V-Gamut primaries, with D65 white point.
TCS_Custom: User defined color space and white point.
